name: Alexandre Manning
introduction: Alexandre Manning is an actor, known for Zoolander, The Cut Runs Deep, and 1095 Days. He is a top model represented by Ford Modeling agency in NYC. His classic good looks & natural charisma have propelled his successful career in print, television & film. He was recenlty the winner of Paper magazines hottestest New Yorkers & destined to be a star from a early age. His mixed nationality gives him a unique edge over the normal hollywood actor. Alexander also speaks 3 languages English, French & Japanese allowing him to work as a actor in 3 markets internationally.
